data.name: labelLoading.Text
data.value:
Characters started from Jagex Launcher will display here when import helper is stopped.
You can import characters from different Jagex accounts by signing out, and into the other account.
Importing is only required for new characters, or to make your life easier if a login token expires.
Accounts that don't use Jagex Launcher must be manually entered in the accounts.csv file.
